t `@Modifying` methods and their automatic transaction management. It seems that criteria like `role` being null or `purchases` being empty are ignored by default. Additionally, I notice pagination is working correctly, sorting users by age and finding usernames with the right conditions. Lastly, I need to ensure there's no import clash with `javax.persistence.EntityGraph`.\"}]}"}, {"type": "text", "text": "Implemented comprehensive Spring Data JPA tests for `org.springframework.data:spring-data-jpa:2.7.18`.\n\nChanged files:\n- `tests/src/org.springframework.data/spring-data-jpa/2.7.18/src/test/java/org_springframework_data/spring_data_jpa/Spring_data_jpaTest.java`\n  - Replaced placeholder with integration-style tests covering:\n    - Spring Data JPA repository proxy creation\n    - CRUD/save/flush\n    - derived queries\n    - `@Query`\n    - `@EntityGraph`\n    - `@Modifying`\n    - specifications\n    - query-by-example\n    - paging/sorting\n    - interface projections\n    - `JpaSort`\n    - JSR-310 JPA converters\n  - Added local test entities, repository, projection, and Spring/JPA configuration.\n\n- `tests/src/org.springframework.data/spring-data-jpa/2.7.18/build.gradle`\n  - Added required test dependencies for meaningful JPA execution:\n    - `com.h2database:h2:2.2.224`\n    - `org.hibernate:hibernate-core:5.6.15.Final`\n\nPer instructions, I did not compile, run, or verify the tests.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0b1209bff4dc5a840169ff3d39dc88819e869fb842677d7da8\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 945, "output": 893, "cacheRead": 40448, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 42286, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1778335022688, "responseId": "resp_0b1209bff4dc5a840169ff3d2fa7d0819e9c112ca73bbeb6cf"}}
